parseFullName

public void parseFullName(ZoologicalName nameToBeFilled,
                          String fullNameString,
                          Rank rank,
                          boolean makeEmpty)
Description copied from interface: ITaxonNameParser
Parses the taxonname String and fills the result into the existing TaxonNameBase nameToBeFilled. Name related fields are set to default (null for Strings and other objects like Authors and References and false for booleans). NameRelations are not changed. If the String is not parseable the "hasProblem" bit is set to true. No change is done to nameToBeFilled if fullName == null.

Specified by:
parseFullName in interface ITaxonNameParser<ZoologicalName>
Parameters:
nameToBeFilled - The TaxonNameBaseToBeFilled
fullNameString - TaxonNameBase with Author, Year, Reference etc.,
